  "intent": "Execute a Zymo Quick-DNA/RNA Viral MagBead extraction protocol using magnetic bead separation. Add 400\u00b5L viral DNA/RNA buffer and 20\u00b5L magnetic binding beads to samples, perform sequential washes with 250\u00b5L wash buffers 1 and 2, followed by dual 250\u00b5L ethanol washes. Air dry beads for 10 minutes, then elute purified nucleic acids with 30\u00b5L DNase/RNase-free water into a clean 96-well PCR plate using magnetic separation at each step.",
